The dirtiest potatoes out there! 

These potatoes were harvested 7 months ago! Because they were grown in heavy clay and kept dirty they still look brand new. 

Red potatoes are the healthiest of any potato. Their skin is filled with fibre, Vitamin B’s, iron and potassium. Red potatoes actually have more potassium than bananas 🍌 

The more you know! #potatoes #farming #spud #redpotato #farm
Today we are painting our potatoes red! We do this because we simply get more money for them 🤞😉Did you know how red potatoes were made? #potato #potatoes #farm #joking

I’m joking!!
You don’t actually suck at storing potatoes 🥺 but if you do, let me help you! 
-Cool Dark Place 
-Ventilation 
-Avoid light
-Don’t wash before storing
-Keep separate from other produce #farming #agriculture #potatoes #farmer #harvest

Update on our land: 

If you are new here we have been trying to save some of the best farmland in all of Canada from being developed

It grows the first potatoes each year in Canada and grows 50 million servings of vegetables at a time when we are relying on foreign imports

I get asked a lot if we won or lost this battle. 
We are currently working with the federal government to save this land, however they said a decision within the next 2-3 years would be a quick one. 

I remain optimistic about keeping this land in agriculture, and will continue working with the political figures in Canada to make sure it does NOT GET PAVED OVER

Thank you for the support, for the over 80,000 signatures on our petition, and for all the engagement and comments of support. We will need you again in the future! #farming #farmers #farmland #agriculture #farmlife #protest

One of the first things I noticed when I came back to the farm was how many potatoes couldn't be sold based on their appearance.

All the while, food banks were being flooded with new families, and farmers were struggling with debt.

That's why I am starting 'Ten Servings' – for every item of clothing sold, we will rescue 10 servings of Ugly Produce and donate them to the food bank, all while offering fair compensation to the farmer, paying them the #1 price for #2 products.

Through conversations with you at Ugly Potato Days, I realized just how much our society needs a company like this.

We don't have a food shortage in the world; we just have a broken system.

If you purchase an item, show up to an Ugly Potato Day, or simply engage with my content, from the bottom of my heart, I want to say thank you, we are all in this together #farmer #foodwaste #agriculture #food

Dirty Thirty

My family threw me a surprise birthday this week for my 30th 

All of the accomplishments in my life fade in comparison to the incredible friends and family that surround me. 

The older I get the more I realize that the quality of your life is largely based on the quality of people you surround yourself with. And I have been blessed to have these friends, family and many more that add value to my daily life.
